![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1c1f76af-d650-4ff2-825c-f11de9b534b1/e348.jpg)

In today’s episode, we’re throwing it back to Sky High (2005), that quirky superhero high school movie you might remember from the mid-2000s. We’re talking about everything from the cool powers to the cheesy teen drama, and whether this nostalgic flick still holds up. Is Sky High as fun as you remember, or does it miss the mark? Tune in as we break it down and share our thoughts on this underrated gem!

Please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us wherever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by **ComicBook Clique**, the only stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.

